<item>
            <title>[SOLR-11057] RangeQuery can overflow in PointFields when quering the type limits</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11057</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This can happen when the upper limit of the range is the lowest value of the type or when the lower limit is the max value of the type. For example:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;q=field_i:{Integer.MAX_VALUE TO Integer.MAX_VALUE]&lt;/tt&gt;. Note that this should not return any docs&lt;/p&gt;</description>
